3.3 Source Code Availability.

If You distribute or make available to others the Covered Software in Executable form, You must also make the Source Code for the Covered Software available to all recipients in a manner that is consistent with the Source Code availability requirements of this License. You may satisfy this obligation in a number of ways:

A. You may provide the Source Code to all recipients along with the Executable.

